{"tid":1510762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［正視聽］可唔可以唔講「我要攬炒」？","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T15:13:18.000Z","uid":104817,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a67eca57976a4e3d5df16ccf49f0ed4575163907","tid":1510762,"uid":104817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"唔係話要否定攬炒呢個方法，但講「我要攬炒」呢一個講法其實唔太合適，並且引人垢病。<br />\n<br />\n英語說法&rdquo;if we burn, you burn with us&rdquo;係話如果你想搞我地既話，我地就攬埋你一齊死。潛台詞係你好快啲收手，唔係攬炒。但如果我哋淨係講「我要攬炒」既話，就好似變左為破壞而破壞，少咗層意思。<br />\n<br />\n子華神都講過公關好重要。可唔可以集思廣益諗個好啲嘅口號？"},{"pid":"d3113d78e18d059af8ef36327d04a9e0f9e9c244","tid":1510762,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攬唔攬炒選擇權係政府，唔係人民。"},{"pid":"bc466fe23971e7f9d542c3a099d1a3baafbaf5f4","tid":1510762,"uid":104817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"自推十次... 1"},{"pid":"a5dce3b2dc51314082488fba0e46eeabe45b051e","tid":1510762,"uid":164387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e39d46776678d22bec3a6c3bacb57f05af1c276","tid":1510762,"uid":104817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:01:16.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9b731e068e3bb0c03f873dea72fe1c5708b3a8e0","tid":1510762,"uid":104817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ba1d424026d1abbb6715cc69b2d822c2094003a1","tid":1510762,"uid":104817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"05756f338af0c191abbbe5631019bc6ec91c251d","tid":1510762,"uid":104817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:01:48.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"708516976ab71b3